metadata.name: Sword type pendant
metadata.description:
Big snake with blue eyes on the rampage, lifting everyone up. Lin Xuan did not have much spiritual force, the body was heavily hit.



Fortunately, he had swallowed the ganoderma ahead of time, and the powerful medicine was healing his wounds, but in spite of that, he was still vomiting blood.



His body fell into the ravine, this fall all his bones are almost broken, the front of the garment dyed red, Lin Xuan did not notice, his blood touched the sword pendant, all weird disappeared.
